message.entry:
Internal Error - "{0}" toolbox is not supported. Please follow the following steps to use the IconRepository class.
 1. Add your toolbox name to the enumeration in matlabshared.testmeasapps.internal.themeableiconrepository.SupportedToolboxes class.
 2. Create an icon repository class (See matlabshared.transportapp.internal.ICTIconRepository for reference).
 3. Add the name of your IconRepository class to the ToolboxIconRepositoryDictionary property in SupportedToolboxes.m.
 e.g. "ict", "matlabshared.transportapp.internal.ICTIconRepository" shows the Icon repository class name for the ICT toolbox.
Icon "{0}" not found for the "{1}" toolbox. Supported icons are -\n{2}\n
